1
00:01:31,780 --> 00:01:41,220
=The Glory=

2
00:01:42,230 --> 00:01:43,190
Hanyan.

3
00:01:44,700 --> 00:01:45,560
Good girl.

4
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,520
Child.

5
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:48,430
Child, you're awake.

6
00:01:48,430 --> 00:01:49,960
You're finally awake.

7
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,550
Slowly, slowly.

8
00:02:01,150 --> 00:02:02,110
Father.

9
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:03,400
Hanyan.

10
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:06,760
Grandmother.

11
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,120
Where am I?

12
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:15,240
Child, it's okay now.

13
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,920
It's all over now.

14
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:20,270
Thanks to our ancestors' grace.

15
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,590
Thanks to you, my good child,

16
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:24,750
our family survived.

17
00:02:25,150 --> 00:02:27,680
You've been unconscious
with a high fever for days.

18
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,920
You scared us all.

19
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,360
Where is Mother?

20
00:02:33,140 --> 00:02:34,960
Your mother is fine.

21
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,400
She discovered the secret passage
in the house

22
00:02:37,990 --> 00:02:39,150
but didn't trust me.

23
00:02:39,150 --> 00:02:41,470
She thought I was Pei's adopted son

24
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:43,480
and caused this trouble.

25
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:46,710
Luckily, Mr. Yan saw through everything
at the last moment

26
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:49,180
and stopped the Supervision
from executing before reporting.

27
00:02:49,180 --> 00:02:51,740
That's how I cleared my name.

28
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:55,060
Given that your mother,
though reckless in her actions,

29
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:57,580
didn't make any major mistakes,

30
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:59,660
she was given a slight reprimand

31
00:02:59,660 --> 00:03:01,340
and wasn't sentenced.

32
00:03:02,540 --> 00:03:04,420
The Judicial Review
has changed the verdict.

33
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:06,780
What about Mr. Yuwen?

34
00:03:07,860 --> 00:03:10,340
I have old grievances with Mr. Yuwen,

35
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:12,500
but they're in the past.

36
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:15,140
We'll sort them out in the future.

37
00:03:15,140 --> 00:03:17,380
After all, there's plenty of time.

38
00:03:17,580 --> 00:03:20,020
You just focus on recuperating.

39
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:22,660
Your health is the top priority now.

40
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:25,820
Now, Zhuang Hanyan,
as the lineal daughter,

41
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:27,800
has quelled the internal strife
at the guild hall

42
00:03:28,020 --> 00:03:30,820
and carried a corpse to save her family
on the execution ground.

43
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:33,460
This is well-known in the Capital.

44
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:37,060
Everyone says that daughters
should be like you.

45
00:03:37,060 --> 00:03:38,540
Not only that.

46
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:39,580
Some people say

47
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:41,380
that wives should be like you.

48
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:42,340
Yes.

49
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:43,540
What are you doing?

50
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:44,900
I want to see Mother.

51
00:03:45,090 --> 00:03:46,420
You silly girl.

52
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:47,290
Slow down.

53
00:03:54,580 --> 00:03:55,580
Madam.

54
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:58,020
Eat something.

55
00:03:59,780 --> 00:04:01,700
It's been heated several times.

56
00:04:03,780 --> 00:04:04,740
Madam.

57
00:04:15,620 --> 00:04:16,580
Let her go.

58
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:19,860
I don't want to see her.

59
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,060
Miss Hanyan,

60
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:24,300
you should go back and rest.

61
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:26,180
The madam also needs to rest.

62
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,060
Mother.

63
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:35,820
You've had your way.

64
00:04:37,980 --> 00:04:39,900
Why do you keep pestering me?

65
00:04:40,660 --> 00:04:43,340
You crippled my legs

66
00:04:43,980 --> 00:04:46,780
and ruined my plans.

67
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:51,140
You're doomed to harm me

68
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:53,140
and ruin my life.

69
00:04:55,820 --> 00:04:56,780
Get lost.

70
00:04:57,780 --> 00:04:59,340
Even if you hate me,

71
00:05:00,340 --> 00:05:01,660
I will never regret it.

72
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:03,180
Get lost!

73
00:05:06,820 --> 00:05:07,740
Get lost!

74
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:08,700
Miss Hanyan.

75
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,980
Miss Hanyan, hurry and leave.

76
00:05:11,020 --> 00:05:12,420
(Flying Swan on Snow)
Miss Hanyan.

77
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:13,380
Just leave.

78
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:15,860
Miss Hanyan.

79
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,260
Don't fixate on this.

80
00:05:17,260 --> 00:05:18,780
What exactly do you want?

81
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:21,020
I just want her to tell me the truth.

82
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:23,060
Come back. Come back.

83
00:05:23,060 --> 00:05:24,660
What are you doing? Let me go.

84
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:25,620
Miss Hanyan.

85
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:31,620
As you two have reached this point,

86
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,780
I really can't bear it.

87
00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:37,100
Since the madam refuses to tell you,

88
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:40,180
I'll take the liberty

89
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:41,420
and tell you the truth

90
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:44,540
that you want to know.

91
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:47,500
Years ago,

92
00:05:48,780 --> 00:05:50,620
when your mother married your father,

93
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:52,780
they had several years

94
00:05:54,580 --> 00:05:57,260
of peaceful life together.

95
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:05,260
=Episode 14=

96
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:08,060
(Peace and Leisure)

97
00:06:08,060 --> 00:06:10,340
(17 years ago)
My wife's belly is pointed.

98
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:11,900
They say it'll be a boy.

99
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:13,100
Physician, what do you think?

100
00:06:15,140 --> 00:06:17,700
The pulse is steady,
and the fetal heartbeat is strong.

101
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:20,820
Perhaps it's time to congratulate you

102
00:06:20,820 --> 00:06:22,460
on having a son.

103
00:06:22,460 --> 00:06:24,300
So, it really is a boy.

104
00:06:24,540 --> 00:06:25,500
That's wonderful.

105
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:26,980
Our family will have an heir.

106
00:06:27,780 --> 00:06:29,220
Mothers and daughters are born close.

107
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:31,060
I hope it's a daughter.

108
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:35,140
Oh, no. Something's wrong.

109
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:37,660
The old master has fainted.

110
00:06:42,220 --> 00:06:46,580
(Yongshou Chamber)

111
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:49,460
Your father's illness is serious.

112
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:51,580
Physician, please try
everything you can.

113
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:54,820
Your father has always been healthy.

114
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:56,500
How could he suddenly fall ill?

115
00:06:56,900 --> 00:06:58,300
Could it be something supernatural?

116
00:07:04,380 --> 00:07:05,940
Go and find out

117
00:07:05,940 --> 00:07:08,880
who the most famous Taoist master
in the Capital is now.

118
00:07:08,890 --> 00:07:10,020
Yes, Ms. Zhou.

119
00:07:16,540 --> 00:07:18,220
May I ask if there have been
any strangers

120
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:20,840
(Seclusion, Zhuang Residence)
in the house in the past half year?

121
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:22,920
Such as new servants

122
00:07:22,980 --> 00:07:24,540
or babies?

123
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:28,660
My wife is about to give birth.

124
00:07:31,780 --> 00:07:33,860
The house is filled with dark energy.

125
00:07:34,940 --> 00:07:37,140
The unborn little master

126
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:39,500
might've been possessed
by a barefoot ghost.

127
00:07:39,980 --> 00:07:43,220
By then, the little master
and his father's lives

128
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:45,900
will be at risk.

129
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:49,380
How can we break this curse?

130
00:07:52,020 --> 00:07:53,980
When the madam gives birth,

131
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:56,500
the barefoot ghost will arrive.

132
00:07:57,660 --> 00:08:00,420
You must strike the baby's feet
with peach wood

133
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:02,460
to drive the evil spirit away.

134
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:04,260
If so, my son will die.

135
00:08:04,260 --> 00:08:05,260
This won't do.

136
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:06,660
Is there no other way

137
00:08:06,660 --> 00:08:07,980
to save my father's life?

138
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:13,260
Harder.

139
00:08:14,340 --> 00:08:15,300
Harder.

140
00:08:16,020 --> 00:08:17,100
One more basin of water.

141
00:08:18,740 --> 00:08:20,540
How is this so coincidental?

142
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:22,420
It has to be a boy.

143
00:08:22,820 --> 00:08:23,780
Harder.

144
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:25,500
Madam, harder.

145
00:08:25,500 --> 00:08:27,220
Only a lineal son can bring

146
00:08:28,140 --> 00:08:29,820
- some hope.
- Harder.

147
00:08:42,780 --> 00:08:44,240
The evil spirit is hard to deal with.

148
00:08:44,380 --> 00:08:46,820
Only the method I told you

149
00:08:46,820 --> 00:08:47,980
can break it.

150
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:50,660
Master, please decide.

151
00:08:58,660 --> 00:08:59,620
Madam,

152
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:01,420
these silly physicians

153
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,340
are wrong.

154
00:09:03,780 --> 00:09:04,980
It's a daughter.

155
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:13,020
A daughter is good.

156
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,560
You were born in the cold winter,

157
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:17,980
so we'll name you Hanyan,

158
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:21,260
hoping that you won't fear the cold

159
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:23,500
and that you'll have a proud spirit,

160
00:09:24,220 --> 00:09:26,580
flying high in the sky.

161
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:36,500
Nanny Chen, what's wrong?

162
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:38,140
Madam,

163
00:09:38,140 --> 00:09:39,820
you nearly had a dystocia just now,

164
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:41,860
so I didn't dare tell you.

165
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:43,860
There's a Taoist priest

166
00:09:44,260 --> 00:09:45,820
in Yongshou Chamber.

167
00:09:49,220 --> 00:09:51,500
The madam has given birth to a daughter.

168
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:53,700
It's a daughter?

169
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:54,660
Yes.

170
00:09:55,740 --> 00:09:56,580
A daughter?

171
00:09:56,810 --> 00:09:58,140
Are you sure?

172
00:09:58,140 --> 00:09:59,300
Is it really not a son?

173
00:09:59,300 --> 00:10:00,500
Absolutely not.

174
00:10:01,540 --> 00:10:03,260
The old master

175
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:05,940
has gone to the heavens.

176
00:10:06,340 --> 00:10:09,060
Everyone, please mourn.

177
00:10:11,300 --> 00:10:12,260
Master...

178
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:14,220
- Master...
- Father...

179
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:16,380
Master...

180
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:17,340
- Master...
- Father...

181
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:18,940
The evil spirit is cruel.

182
00:10:19,060 --> 00:10:22,140
Killing the old master
is just the beginning.

183
00:10:22,140 --> 00:10:24,460
If we don't remove this barefoot ghost,

184
00:10:25,020 --> 00:10:26,860
the house will be in danger,

185
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:28,620
and the madam

186
00:10:28,620 --> 00:10:30,860
and her daughter just born

187
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:33,220
will also be at risk.

188
00:10:36,900 --> 00:10:37,860
This...

189
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:40,740
Where is that barking Taoist priest?

190
00:10:40,900 --> 00:10:41,900
Let me kill him.

191
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:43,260
Madam, Madam!

192
00:10:43,460 --> 00:10:44,420
Madam!

193
00:10:44,820 --> 00:10:46,380
You've just given birth.

194
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:47,820
Please don't act impulsively.

195
00:10:48,140 --> 00:10:49,100
Madam,

196
00:10:49,420 --> 00:10:51,300
someone must've secretly resented you

197
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:53,660
and set up such a deadly trap early on.

198
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:57,540
Zhou Ruyin.

199
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:02,980
Nanny Chen, hurry.

200
00:11:11,580 --> 00:11:12,540
Move aside.

201
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:15,900
Madam, the doors have been locked tight.

202
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:18,180
The master is waiting for you
in Jianjia Chamber.

203
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:33,700
Mother.

204
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:35,700
Mother.

205
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:37,140
Mother, please.

206
00:11:37,140 --> 00:11:39,220
Please save my poor child.

207
00:11:39,980 --> 00:11:42,020
She's your granddaughter.

208
00:11:42,260 --> 00:11:44,740
- Please plead for her.
- Bodhisattva, help us.

209
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:46,420
- Mother, please.
- Bodhisattva, help us.

210
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:48,480
- Open the door, Mother.
- Bodhisattva, help us.

211
00:11:48,540 --> 00:11:50,220
- Please save her.
- Bodhisattva, help us.

212
00:11:50,220 --> 00:11:52,180
I'm willing to be vegetarian for life

213
00:11:52,180 --> 00:11:54,460
and transcribe
and chant sutras every day

214
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:55,900
to pray for you.

215
00:11:56,020 --> 00:11:58,100
Please save her.

216
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:00,740
Mother, open the door.

217
00:12:00,740 --> 00:12:01,860
I beg you.

218
00:12:03,420 --> 00:12:06,340
(Gongtong Chamber)

219
00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:07,340
Zhou Ruyin.

220
00:12:07,340 --> 00:12:09,060
Zhou Ruyin, I beg you.

221
00:12:09,260 --> 00:12:11,180
I beg you to save my child.

222
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:12,220
Zhou Ruyin.

223
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:15,580
Zhou Ruyin, open the door.

224
00:12:15,780 --> 00:12:17,980
I beg you to save my child.

225
00:12:20,020 --> 00:12:21,180
From now on,

226
00:12:21,340 --> 00:12:23,020
I will serve you for the rest of my life

227
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:24,220
as your servant

228
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,380
without complaint.

229
00:12:25,940 --> 00:12:28,220
Zhou Ruyin, open the door.

230
00:12:28,900 --> 00:12:30,860
You like my jewelry box, right?

231
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:31,820
You can take it.

232
00:12:31,980 --> 00:12:32,940
You can take

233
00:12:33,130 --> 00:12:34,000
whatever you want

234
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,700
from me.

235
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:38,730
I just want my child to live, okay?

236
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:41,440
- The child is innocent.
- Don't be afraid.

237
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:43,540
- You're also a mother.
- Don't be afraid.

238
00:12:43,780 --> 00:12:44,740
Can't you save

239
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:46,260
an infant?

240
00:12:46,260 --> 00:12:47,300
Zhou Ruyin.

241
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:49,860
I'll kowtow to you.

242
00:12:50,180 --> 00:12:52,940
Zhou Ruyin, I'll kowtow to you.

243
00:12:53,860 --> 00:12:55,180
Zhou Ruyin.

244
00:12:57,020 --> 00:12:58,740
Zhou Ruyin,

245
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:01,340
please save my child.

246
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:03,300
Madam!

247
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:05,980
Barefoot ghost, show yourself.

248
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:11,060
Zhuang Shiyang,

249
00:13:12,020 --> 00:13:14,420
for the sake of our marriage,

250
00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:19,500
let me and my daughter have a way out.

251
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:22,460
I swear I will leave with her,

252
00:13:23,140 --> 00:13:25,260
never to set foot in the house again.

253
00:13:25,260 --> 00:13:26,220
Xiwen,

254
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:29,180
the Taoist master is driving away evil.

255
00:13:29,300 --> 00:13:31,140
He's doing this
to save the child's life.

256
00:13:31,820 --> 00:13:32,940
Hand her over.

257
00:13:33,340 --> 00:13:35,100
She has just been born.

258
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:37,260
Have you considered the consequences

259
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:40,060
of using that peach wood stick on her?

260
00:13:40,540 --> 00:13:42,420
She's also your daughter.

261
00:13:43,340 --> 00:13:44,540
I beg you.

262
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:46,300
I know she is our daughter.

263
00:13:46,300 --> 00:13:47,580
I would never harm her.

264
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:48,780
Please trust me.

265
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:56,340
You filthy Taoist.

266
00:13:57,100 --> 00:13:59,740
On what grounds do you say
my daughter is a barefoot ghost?

267
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:01,020
Tell me.

268
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:03,940
You mortals can't see

269
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:05,960
the evil black energy

270
00:14:05,970 --> 00:14:07,580
swirling around Jianjia Chamber,

271
00:14:08,060 --> 00:14:11,100
but I can see it clearly.

272
00:14:11,340 --> 00:14:12,740
But I heard

273
00:14:12,900 --> 00:14:14,020
that when you arrived,

274
00:14:14,180 --> 00:14:16,340
you said the evil spirit
was a young master.

275
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:19,900
It doesn't matter
if it's a boy or a girl.

276
00:14:20,020 --> 00:14:21,460
You couldn't even tell the gender

277
00:14:21,460 --> 00:14:23,100
through the belly,

278
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:24,660
and now you dare to swindle us,

279
00:14:24,660 --> 00:14:25,980
saying you can tell it's a ghost?

280
00:14:25,980 --> 00:14:27,740
What a joke.

281
00:14:27,740 --> 00:14:28,700
Mr. Zhuang,

282
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:32,060
your wife has lost her sanity
because of the barefoot ghost.

283
00:14:32,420 --> 00:14:34,060
I must offend her now.

