560
00:28:39,420 --> 00:28:40,780
If you have a reason,

561
00:28:40,980 --> 00:28:42,980
you can tell me openly.

562
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:44,540
I'll find a way

563
00:28:44,540 --> 00:28:46,980
to help you with your troubles.

564
00:28:48,180 --> 00:28:49,140
Hanyan,

565
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:52,500
offer your incense to your grandfather

566
00:28:57,740 --> 00:28:59,060
and tell your grandfather

567
00:28:59,550 --> 00:29:00,660
you've grown up.

568
00:29:01,350 --> 00:29:02,580
You are

569
00:29:02,740 --> 00:29:05,980
the most accomplished child
of our family.

570
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:23,900
(Spirit Tablet of Zhuang Hanliang)

571
00:29:25,020 --> 00:29:26,180
Father, you're right.

572
00:29:26,780 --> 00:29:28,100
The future of our family

573
00:29:28,220 --> 00:29:29,700
is the most important.

574
00:29:30,220 --> 00:29:31,500
Since you

575
00:29:31,620 --> 00:29:33,180
recognize my ability,

576
00:29:33,300 --> 00:29:36,420
please let me take charge
of the household

577
00:29:37,760 --> 00:29:38,980
to relieve you of your burdens.

578
00:29:40,260 --> 00:29:42,780
You've been in Danzhou for many years

579
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:45,420
and have not undergone
the hair pinning ceremony,

580
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:47,300
which is against the rituals.

581
00:29:47,300 --> 00:29:48,540
Then please, Father,

582
00:29:48,540 --> 00:29:50,380
hold the hair pinning ceremony for me,

583
00:29:50,620 --> 00:29:52,700
and then let me take charge.

584
00:29:57,580 --> 00:30:00,000
Recently, the Hanlin Academy
has had a major task to handle.

585
00:30:00,020 --> 00:30:00,980
I'm afraid

586
00:30:01,700 --> 00:30:03,940
I may not be able to spare a moment.

587
00:30:04,220 --> 00:30:05,460
What major task?

588
00:30:05,700 --> 00:30:07,500
A Western scholar

589
00:30:07,660 --> 00:30:09,380
has come across the seas

590
00:30:09,860 --> 00:30:12,660
to exchange knowledge with us

591
00:30:12,980 --> 00:30:14,340
so we can learn from each other.

592
00:30:14,700 --> 00:30:17,060
The Hanlin Academy is in charge of this,

593
00:30:17,420 --> 00:30:19,980
and I've been appointed
to attend to him.

594
00:30:20,220 --> 00:30:21,900
Together with my colleagues,

595
00:30:22,220 --> 00:30:24,380
I will compile

596
00:30:24,380 --> 00:30:26,340
this scholar's lifetime of learning

597
00:30:27,180 --> 00:30:28,660
into the Comprehensive Encyclopedia.

598
00:30:28,700 --> 00:30:30,540
As for the hair pinning ceremony,

599
00:30:31,290 --> 00:30:33,260
- I think...
- Since you're busy,

600
00:30:33,260 --> 00:30:34,540
let Mother

601
00:30:34,540 --> 00:30:35,780
handle the ceremony.

602
00:30:37,380 --> 00:30:38,340
Good.

603
00:30:38,820 --> 00:30:39,780
Very good.

604
00:30:40,100 --> 00:30:41,500
I'll leave it to your mother.

605
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:43,140
Thank you, Father.

606
00:30:52,820 --> 00:30:54,780
(Hanlin Academy)

607
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:05,940
(Complete Map of the World)

608
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:21,740
(Comprehensive Encyclopedia)

609
00:31:23,340 --> 00:31:26,740
(Few days later)

610
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:28,540
(Seclusion, Zhuang Residence)

611
00:31:30,620 --> 00:31:33,540
My daughter, Hanyan, is virtuous.

612
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:36,940
This auspicious day is chosen
to invite guests

613
00:31:36,940 --> 00:31:39,500
for her hair pinning ceremony.

614
00:31:54,060 --> 00:31:55,580
First, bow.

615
00:32:10,260 --> 00:32:12,020
Second, wear hairpins.

616
00:32:58,700 --> 00:33:00,060
Third, wear a robe.

617
00:34:00,180 --> 00:34:01,700
The hair pinning ceremony is complete.

618
00:34:02,140 --> 00:34:03,380
Today, I will

619
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:07,020
let you take charge of the family.

620
00:34:07,580 --> 00:34:10,500
I hope that you will follow
the right path,

621
00:34:11,140 --> 00:34:13,820
be kind and virtuous,
and live a peaceful life.

622
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:18,300
Though dull, I'll remember this.

623
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:21,820
Madam,

624
00:34:21,980 --> 00:34:23,420
someone from the Palace has come.

625
00:34:23,420 --> 00:34:25,180
They say they bring
a congratulatory gift

626
00:34:25,180 --> 00:34:27,980
from Noble Consort Miao for Miss Hanyan.

627
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:35,460
Even the Palace knows

628
00:34:35,460 --> 00:34:36,740
about Miss Zhuang Hanyan?

629
00:34:37,180 --> 00:34:38,340
You didn't know this?

630
00:34:38,340 --> 00:34:40,540
Years ago, there were two beauties
in the Capital,

631
00:34:40,540 --> 00:34:42,380
both from distinguished families.

632
00:34:42,580 --> 00:34:45,140
One became the favored
Noble Consort Miao,

633
00:34:45,140 --> 00:34:47,260
while the other became the madam
of the Zhuang family.

634
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:50,460
They were inseparable like sisters.

635
00:34:50,460 --> 00:34:52,060
It was a well-known story back then.

636
00:34:56,740 --> 00:34:58,420
Mother, you're friends

637
00:34:58,420 --> 00:34:59,660
with a Noble Consort?

638
00:35:00,460 --> 00:35:01,900
Just old friends.

639
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:04,180
She's in that complicated Palace,

640
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:06,300
and I've been hidden
in the inner chambers.

641
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:08,140
We haven't met in a long time.

642
00:35:12,740 --> 00:35:13,700
Xiwen.

643
00:35:17,980 --> 00:35:20,020
Miss Hanyan, congratulations
on your hair pinning.

644
00:35:21,900 --> 00:35:23,300
Thank you, Mr. Yuwen.

645
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:27,700
I heard

646
00:35:27,860 --> 00:35:29,420
that you were suspended by His Majesty.

647
00:35:34,580 --> 00:35:35,460
I thought

648
00:35:35,460 --> 00:35:37,380
that if you could handle
the Pei faction case,

649
00:35:37,940 --> 00:35:39,420
you'd surely be promoted,

650
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:42,660
but in the end, I dragged you down.

651
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:45,340
I've grown tired of the ups

652
00:35:45,740 --> 00:35:47,140
and downs of officialdom.

653
00:35:48,300 --> 00:35:49,660
Taking this opportunity

654
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:52,180
to leave this place
of strife seems best.

655
00:35:54,460 --> 00:35:55,940
But in the Capital,

656
00:35:59,020 --> 00:36:01,180
there is still someone
I can't let go of.

657
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:06,820
Mr. Yuwen, are you planning
to leave the Capital?

658
00:36:09,260 --> 00:36:10,660
That's indeed my plan.

659
00:36:11,180 --> 00:36:12,140
Xiwen,

660
00:36:13,020 --> 00:36:15,020
could you help me decide?

661
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:18,140
This is serious.

662
00:36:19,140 --> 00:36:21,020
How could I make the decision for you?

663
00:36:22,940 --> 00:36:24,500
If you've made up your mind,

664
00:36:25,690 --> 00:36:28,060
I'll wish you peace and success
in the future.

665
00:36:29,460 --> 00:36:31,820
Thank you for all your help these years.

666
00:36:34,380 --> 00:36:35,340
Xiwen,

667
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:39,420
don't you understand my feelings?

668
00:36:41,860 --> 00:36:43,380
I've wasted half my life.

669
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:47,100
It's too late now.

670
00:36:47,540 --> 00:36:49,220
So what?

671
00:36:49,780 --> 00:36:51,340
You still have a chance to choose.

672
00:36:51,340 --> 00:36:52,300
Mr. Yuwen,

673
00:36:52,580 --> 00:36:53,780
please behave yourself.

674
00:36:57,660 --> 00:36:58,620
I'm sorry.

675
00:37:00,380 --> 00:37:01,900
I must take my leave now.

676
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:24,260
Mother, are you truly unwilling

677
00:37:24,460 --> 00:37:25,940
to give yourself another chance?

678
00:37:27,140 --> 00:37:28,700
Don't mention this again.

679
00:37:48,580 --> 00:37:54,220
(Spirit Tablet of Zhuang Hanliang)

680
00:38:10,060 --> 00:38:12,140
Mr. Fu, why bring me here?

681
00:38:12,140 --> 00:38:13,100
What do you want?

682
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:15,100
The residence is lively today.

683
00:38:15,610 --> 00:38:17,730
Only the ancestral hall is still quiet.

684
00:38:18,530 --> 00:38:20,500
What do you want to discuss?

685
00:38:20,500 --> 00:38:21,940
Have you and your father

686
00:38:21,940 --> 00:38:24,100
talked again about the adopted son case?

687
00:38:25,380 --> 00:38:26,500
He only said

688
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:27,980
that the words in prison

689
00:38:28,180 --> 00:38:29,540
were to save the family.

690
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:31,300
Do you believe that?

691
00:38:31,820 --> 00:38:32,980
I only know

692
00:38:33,380 --> 00:38:35,500
that your mind is full of schemes,

693
00:38:35,620 --> 00:38:37,900
and you often put people's families
in jeopardy.

694
00:38:38,660 --> 00:38:40,460
I can no longer trust you.

695
00:38:40,700 --> 00:38:42,140
When you were unconscious,

696
00:38:42,740 --> 00:38:45,220
Zhuang Shiyang was questioned
by the Judicial Review.

697
00:38:45,580 --> 00:38:47,660
He also said it was to save the family.

698
00:39:04,780 --> 00:39:06,700
This is called
the Soul-Settling Incense.

699
00:39:06,820 --> 00:39:08,020
It's rare among common people.

700
00:39:08,220 --> 00:39:10,020
Ordinary families would never use it

701
00:39:10,140 --> 00:39:11,540
to honor their ancestors.

702
00:39:11,540 --> 00:39:13,180
Miss Hanyan, do you know why?

703
00:39:17,670 --> 00:39:19,460
Because it's specifically used

704
00:39:19,620 --> 00:39:21,340
to suppress vengeful spirits.

705
00:39:24,020 --> 00:39:25,900
Light it in front of the spirit tablet,

706
00:39:26,020 --> 00:39:27,900
and it prevents those who died unjustly

707
00:39:27,900 --> 00:39:29,940
from reincarnating or causing trouble.

708
00:39:29,940 --> 00:39:31,660
Mr. Zhuang has been

709
00:39:31,660 --> 00:39:32,900
using it these years to suppress

710
00:39:33,340 --> 00:39:35,820
(Spirit Tablet of Zhuang Hanliang)
your grandfather's spirit.

711
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:39,760
You were framed as a barefoot ghost

712
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:42,180
precisely when your grandfather
fell ill.

713
00:39:42,180 --> 00:39:44,820
Do you think these events
are coincidences?

714
00:40:00,340 --> 00:40:01,340
These

715
00:40:02,460 --> 00:40:04,300
are just your speculations.

716
00:40:04,460 --> 00:40:05,900
You're not a fool.

717
00:40:06,940 --> 00:40:08,180
You must have noticed

718
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:10,260
that Zhuang Shiyang
is definitely not as weak

719
00:40:10,260 --> 00:40:11,780
and simple as he seems.

720
00:40:12,060 --> 00:40:13,020
But you're afraid.

721
00:40:13,340 --> 00:40:14,760
You're afraid to uncover the truth.

722
00:40:15,100 --> 00:40:16,860
If Zhuang Shiyang is Pei's adopted son,

723
00:40:16,860 --> 00:40:19,020
the whole family will be implicated,

724
00:40:19,020 --> 00:40:21,220
and everyone will have to die again,

725
00:40:21,220 --> 00:40:22,180
including

726
00:40:23,020 --> 00:40:24,300
the one you care about most.

727
00:40:27,580 --> 00:40:28,900
But have you thought about it?

728
00:40:29,140 --> 00:40:30,900
The adopted son case
is still unresolved.

729
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:32,420
After this incident,

730
00:40:32,700 --> 00:40:34,500
the Palace will send more people

731
00:40:34,500 --> 00:40:36,460
to investigate quickly and thoroughly.

732
00:40:36,700 --> 00:40:37,940
If I were you,

733
00:40:38,660 --> 00:40:40,220
I wouldn't avoid it;

734
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:41,820
I would take the initiative

735
00:40:41,820 --> 00:40:43,940
and find the evidence faster
than the Judicial Review,

736
00:40:43,940 --> 00:40:45,420
the Supervision, and the Palace.

737
00:40:45,420 --> 00:40:46,380
Only then can you

738
00:40:46,940 --> 00:40:48,860
be prepared for the consequences.

739
00:40:49,580 --> 00:40:50,900
What do you mean

740
00:40:51,660 --> 00:40:53,140
by telling me this?

741
00:40:53,420 --> 00:40:54,380
We should cooperate.

742
00:40:54,700 --> 00:40:55,660
What do you mean?

743
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:57,400
Because of Wu Youzhi's case,

744
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:59,120
I've been suspended
by the Judicial Review.

745
00:40:59,180 --> 00:41:01,140
If you and I work together
to uncover evidence

746
00:41:01,140 --> 00:41:02,740
and send Zhuang Shiyang to prison,

747
00:41:02,860 --> 00:41:04,820
I can earn merits
and restore my position,

748
00:41:05,380 --> 00:41:07,060
and you can take your revenge

749
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,660
without implicating your family.

750
00:41:14,780 --> 00:41:15,940
I know

751
00:41:15,940 --> 00:41:17,460
that my father is somewhat strange,

752
00:41:18,020 --> 00:41:20,980
but do you truly believe
he's the adopted son?

753
00:41:21,310 --> 00:41:24,080
Zhuang Shiyang bought
Wu Youzhi's villa three years ago.

754
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:26,340
Wu Youzhi was a Pei faction member

755
00:41:26,340 --> 00:41:27,500
from Yinan.

756
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:29,540
Could all of this be a coincidence?

757
00:41:33,250 --> 00:41:33,700
Or what?

758
00:41:33,700 --> 00:41:35,880
Though both your father
and grandfather are officials,

759
00:41:35,940 --> 00:41:37,620
you're not a family of great wealth.

760
00:41:38,180 --> 00:41:40,260
Three years ago,
Zhuang Shiyang spent a lot

761
00:41:40,260 --> 00:41:41,980
on this luxurious residence.

762
00:41:42,740 --> 00:41:44,740
He must have had plans from the start.

763
00:41:45,220 --> 00:41:46,340
If the secret passage

764
00:41:46,340 --> 00:41:47,700
is ever exposed in the future,

765
00:41:47,700 --> 00:41:49,700
everything can be blamed on Wu Youzhi.

766
00:41:50,020 --> 00:41:50,980
Even

767
00:41:51,580 --> 00:41:53,580
when they recruited that foolish Duke

768
00:41:53,580 --> 00:41:54,980
into the Zuohang Gang,

769
00:41:55,240 --> 00:41:56,620
they must have intended to use him

770
00:41:56,620 --> 00:41:59,340
as a shield and a scapegoat
for the adopted son.

771
00:42:02,540 --> 00:42:04,220
Do you really think

772
00:42:05,540 --> 00:42:06,620
my father

773
00:42:07,620 --> 00:42:09,420
could have such a cunning plan?

774
00:42:10,020 --> 00:42:12,420
To be taken as an adopted son
by Pei Dafu,

775
00:42:12,780 --> 00:42:14,180
he's certainly no ordinary person.

776
00:42:16,740 --> 00:42:18,740
I'm just a woman
from the inner chambers.

777
00:42:19,340 --> 00:42:20,940
Why must you involve me?

778
00:42:22,120 --> 00:42:24,860
You saw through the plans
I've laid out for so long.

779
00:42:25,460 --> 00:42:28,140
You're no ordinary woman
from the inner chambers.

780
00:42:28,140 --> 00:42:29,580
Besides, you're the lineal daughter

781
00:42:29,580 --> 00:42:31,540
favored by Zhuang Shiyang now,

782
00:42:32,260 --> 00:42:33,700
so you're my first choice.

783
00:42:35,420 --> 00:42:38,140
He is still my father.

784
00:42:39,020 --> 00:42:40,300
Do you think

785
00:42:40,740 --> 00:42:42,060
I would agree to your proposal?

786
00:42:44,180 --> 00:42:46,340
That will depend on how you decide.

787
00:42:46,340 --> 00:42:48,140
I can say no more.

788
00:42:48,140 --> 00:42:49,220
If you're interested,

789
00:42:49,220 --> 00:42:50,700
you can come find me at any time.

790
00:42:59,420 --> 00:43:01,100
(Spirit Tablet of Zhuang Hanliang)

791
00:43:05,500 --> 00:43:08,660
(Kindness Benefits Children)

792
00:43:08,660 --> 00:43:10,220
Miss, why have you hidden here?

793
00:43:10,740 --> 00:43:12,180
Ms. Zhou is looking for you,

794
00:43:12,540 --> 00:43:14,420
saying she'll give you
the household keys.

795
00:43:17,260 --> 00:43:19,460
Let's go. Time to meet her.

796
00:43:19,780 --> 00:43:20,740
Let's go.

797
00:43:20,760 --> 00:43:22,220
(Housekeeping Records of the Zhuangs)

798
00:43:22,220 --> 00:43:23,180
Miss Hanyan,

799
00:43:23,460 --> 00:43:26,260
here are the household keys
and the ledgers.

800
00:43:26,620 --> 00:43:28,820
If there's anything you need help with,

801
00:43:29,100 --> 00:43:30,820
just let me know.

802
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:32,660
I won't be polite, then.

803
00:43:32,660 --> 00:43:35,260
I was just about
to ask you for Nanny Tao.

804
00:43:37,100 --> 00:43:39,020
I've heard Nanny Tao
is loyal and capable.

805
00:43:39,140 --> 00:43:40,860
I've always noticed that.

806
00:43:40,860 --> 00:43:42,660
Ms. Zhou, are you willing
to part with her?

807
00:43:43,940 --> 00:43:44,900
Ms. Zhou,

808
00:43:45,140 --> 00:43:46,180
save me.

809
00:43:46,180 --> 00:43:47,620
If I fall into Miss Hanyan's hands,

810
00:43:48,060 --> 00:43:49,820
how will I survive?

811
00:43:50,180 --> 00:43:51,780
Ms. Zhou, save me.

812
00:43:51,980 --> 00:43:53,540
Miss Hanyan choosing you

813
00:43:53,540 --> 00:43:55,100
is your blessing.

814
00:43:55,540 --> 00:43:56,980
We are both servants.

815
00:43:56,980 --> 00:43:59,100
Now that Miss Hanyan is in charge,

816
00:43:59,300 --> 00:44:01,460
what Miss Hanyan says goes.

817
00:44:01,900 --> 00:44:03,180
Nanny Tao, you must be joking.

818
00:44:03,860 --> 00:44:06,140
I won't sell you off.

819
00:44:06,660 --> 00:44:07,860
Miss Hanyan,

820
00:44:08,620 --> 00:44:10,740
what's your plan for me?

821
00:44:10,740 --> 00:44:12,660
How about you go to Jianjia Chamber

822
00:44:12,660 --> 00:44:14,540
and work under Nanny Chen?

823
00:44:18,820 --> 00:44:21,180
Nanny Tao, please follow me.

824
00:44:24,940 --> 00:44:25,900
Ms. Zhou.

825
00:44:26,260 --> 00:44:27,260
Ms. Zhou.

826
00:44:27,260 --> 00:44:28,340
Save me.

827
00:44:28,340 --> 00:44:29,540
Ms. Zhou, save me.

828
00:44:41,780 --> 00:44:42,980
Thank you, Ms. Zhou.

829
00:44:42,980 --> 00:44:44,940
I will take my leave now.

830
00:44:45,460 --> 00:44:46,820
Miss Hanyan, take care.

831
00:44:52,300 --> 00:44:53,260
Miss Hanyan.

832
00:44:53,660 --> 00:44:55,140
Is there anything else?

833
00:44:57,760 --> 00:44:59,820
Yuchi is young and inexperienced.

834
00:44:59,940 --> 00:45:01,060
After this incident,

835
00:45:01,180 --> 00:45:03,540
he won't be presumptuous anymore.

836
00:45:03,540 --> 00:45:06,060
From now on, I will teach him properly.

837
00:45:06,570 --> 00:45:08,860
Now, in this vast residence,

838
00:45:08,860 --> 00:45:10,900
you're in charge of everything.

839
00:45:11,310 --> 00:45:13,750
I hope you will show magnanimity.

840
00:45:14,190 --> 00:45:15,500
As for the past...

841
00:45:15,500 --> 00:45:17,340
As I'm in charge of the house,

842
00:45:17,540 --> 00:45:19,580
fairness comes first in all matters.

843
00:45:20,140 --> 00:45:21,380
You need not worry.

844
00:45:21,540 --> 00:45:22,540
Yes, yes.

845
00:45:22,780 --> 00:45:24,340
I shouldn't have said that.

846
00:45:31,460 --> 00:45:33,340
This is a rare wild ginseng.

847
00:45:33,740 --> 00:45:35,860
Go send it to Yuzhu Manor.

848
00:45:36,220 --> 00:45:37,740
Be sure to do it respectfully

849
00:45:37,740 --> 00:45:39,900
and thank Miss Hanyan for saving us.

850
00:45:40,100 --> 00:45:42,020
Yes, I will go right now.

851
00:45:44,220 --> 00:45:45,340
You fool.

852
00:45:45,500 --> 00:45:46,820
If you want to go, go yourself.

853
00:45:46,820 --> 00:45:48,180
I can't be bothered to please her.

854
00:45:48,580 --> 00:45:49,540
Come on.

855
00:45:49,900 --> 00:45:52,420
She's in charge of the family now.

856
00:45:52,420 --> 00:45:53,860
Can't you understand?

857
00:45:54,140 --> 00:45:55,980
As long as Father is willing
to support me,

858
00:45:55,980 --> 00:45:57,140
I'm not afraid of her.

859
00:45:58,740 --> 00:46:00,100
She's no longer that wild girl

860
00:46:00,100 --> 00:46:02,260
from Danzhou.

861
00:46:02,580 --> 00:46:04,380
We can't defeat her now.

862
00:46:04,980 --> 00:46:06,580
We have to lie low for now

863
00:46:06,860 --> 00:46:08,100
and wait for the right moment.

864
00:46:08,100 --> 00:46:09,060
Yes.

865
00:46:09,780 --> 00:46:12,300
She claims to clear our family's name,

866
00:46:12,870 --> 00:46:14,980
but Father was never
that old eunuch's adopted son.

867
00:46:14,980 --> 00:46:15,940
Shut up.

868
00:46:16,900 --> 00:46:18,420
Both of you remember:

869
00:46:18,580 --> 00:46:21,300
Never bring up
the adopted son matter again,

870
00:46:22,460 --> 00:46:23,420
especially

871
00:46:24,260 --> 00:46:26,180
not in front of your father.

872
00:46:29,980 --> 00:46:32,020
Yuchi, go and try to persuade her.

873
00:46:48,780 --> 00:46:49,740
Yushan.

874
00:46:50,900 --> 00:46:52,020
Alright, Yushan.

875
00:46:52,460 --> 00:46:53,460
Don't be angry.

876
00:46:54,060 --> 00:46:55,540
What Mom said

877
00:46:55,660 --> 00:46:56,700
is not without reason.

878
00:46:56,900 --> 00:46:57,740
I just can't stand

879
00:46:57,740 --> 00:46:59,620
how she's been running wild over us.

880
00:47:00,980 --> 00:47:02,140
Just endure it.

881
00:47:02,940 --> 00:47:04,700
Right now, she's above us.

882
00:47:05,180 --> 00:47:06,980
Why bother fighting a losing battle?

883
00:47:06,980 --> 00:47:09,260
There are many noble ladies
in the Capital

884
00:47:09,740 --> 00:47:11,900
who can't stand her.

885
00:47:12,240 --> 00:47:13,660
I may not be able to defeat her,

886
00:47:14,370 --> 00:47:17,300
but someone will be able
to deal with her.

887
00:47:42,580 --> 00:47:44,060
(Housekeeping Records of the Zhuangs)

888
00:47:57,540 --> 00:47:58,980
When Mother was in charge,

889
00:47:59,380 --> 00:48:01,580
was it this troublesome
and tiring every day?

890
00:48:01,900 --> 00:48:03,860
The madam knew this was hard work,

891
00:48:04,180 --> 00:48:05,420
so she sent me

892
00:48:05,420 --> 00:48:07,220
to serve you.

893
00:48:12,700 --> 00:48:13,660
Miss Hanyan,

894
00:48:13,660 --> 00:48:15,460
someone entrusted me
with this invitation

895
00:48:15,700 --> 00:48:17,620
to invite you
to the Lantern Festival banquet.

896
00:48:18,020 --> 00:48:19,340
I have no friends in the Capital.

897
00:48:19,340 --> 00:48:20,420
Who would invite me?

898
00:48:22,260 --> 00:48:24,380
(To Miss Zhuang Hanyan)

899
00:48:27,150 --> 00:48:28,780
This invitation says that the lady

900
00:48:28,780 --> 00:48:31,540
should attend with her mother.

901
00:48:31,940 --> 00:48:34,260
They want to make a fool
of Mother and me.

902
00:48:34,260 --> 00:48:35,260
This...

903
00:48:35,260 --> 00:48:37,580
Miss Hanyan, you must not fall
into their trap.

904
00:48:43,380 --> 00:48:44,740
This banquet

905
00:48:47,380 --> 00:48:48,900
may be an opportunity.

906
00:48:51,020 --> 00:48:54,220
(Light, Fu Residence)

907
00:49:00,900 --> 00:49:02,940
My Lord, Mr. Jiang of Chaling Tavern

908
00:49:02,940 --> 00:49:04,180
sent a letter.

909
00:49:04,700 --> 00:49:05,700
Lingzhi, you write.

910
00:49:07,500 --> 00:49:09,540
(To Vice Minister Fu Yunxi)

911
00:49:10,780 --> 00:49:11,820
Hand.

912
00:49:13,020 --> 00:49:14,220
Hand.

913
00:49:14,220 --> 00:49:17,060
(I'd like to meet you in Hongyun Hall.)

914
00:49:17,780 --> 00:49:18,980
Who would like to meet me?

915
00:49:19,220 --> 00:49:21,580
Mr. Jiang said
it was Miss Zhuang Hanyan.

916
00:49:38,380 --> 00:49:40,500
Miss Hanyan, you're eager to meet me.

917
00:49:40,740 --> 00:49:41,860
Have you made up your mind?

918
00:49:43,540 --> 00:49:45,820
Before that, we should work together.

919
00:49:46,420 --> 00:49:48,020
Mr. Fu, I wonder if you'd be willing

920
00:49:48,020 --> 00:49:49,420
to join me in this matter.

921
00:50:13,091 --> 00:50:15,901
♪She hides away her past♪

922
00:50:16,181 --> 00:50:18,511
♪Covered in scars♪

923
00:50:20,861 --> 00:50:23,621
♪She forgets who she is♪

924
00:50:23,991 --> 00:50:26,251
♪Disguised as one returning home♪

925
00:50:27,611 --> 00:50:30,951
♪When night falls, in the yard♪

926
00:50:30,951 --> 00:50:33,891
♪Mist rises in swirls♪

927
00:50:35,351 --> 00:50:38,521
♪She steps onto the battlefield♪

928
00:50:38,801 --> 00:50:42,621
♪No distraction is allowed♪

929
00:50:43,961 --> 00:50:47,021
♪A touch of love, a trace of hate♪

930
00:50:47,281 --> 00:50:49,791
♪No need to question♪

931
00:50:51,681 --> 00:50:54,661
♪The truth and falsehood♪

932
00:50:54,661 --> 00:50:57,751
♪Needs to be discerned♪

933
00:50:58,511 --> 00:51:01,851
♪Seeking warmth in peril♪

934
00:51:01,851 --> 00:51:06,191
♪Only to be mocked as naive♪

935
00:51:06,311 --> 00:51:09,661
♪War drums sound, beacons flare♪

936
00:51:09,661 --> 00:51:13,531
♪Who can break free♪

937
00:51:13,971 --> 00:51:16,431
♪She is willing to become a blade♪

938
00:51:16,431 --> 00:51:18,381
♪Moving forward without retreat♪

939
00:51:18,381 --> 00:51:21,661
♪Charging into this lonely fortress♪

940
00:51:21,661 --> 00:51:24,231
♪Even in a fateful clash♪

941
00:51:24,231 --> 00:51:26,051
♪With eyes stained with blood♪

942
00:51:26,051 --> 00:51:29,301
♪She holds no grudge♪

943
00:51:29,511 --> 00:51:31,871
♪She does not trust fate♪

944
00:51:31,871 --> 00:51:33,911
♪She does not pray to gods♪

945
00:51:33,911 --> 00:51:37,101
♪She grips the blade♪

946
00:51:37,231 --> 00:51:39,701
♪As geese fly south in winter♪

947
00:51:39,701 --> 00:51:41,621
♪She alone journeys north♪

948
00:51:41,621 --> 00:51:48,611
♪Seeking truth in falsehood♪

949
00:51:49,181 --> 00:51:51,461
♪She'd become the blade♪

950
00:51:51,661 --> 00:51:53,431
♪With love as her shield♪

951
00:51:53,431 --> 00:51:56,731
♪Plunging into this mortal world♪

952
00:51:56,931 --> 00:51:59,311
♪Shattering mirages♪

953
00:51:59,311 --> 00:52:01,161
♪And illusions♪

954
00:52:01,161 --> 00:52:04,641
♪To pay respect to the fallen souls♪

955
00:52:04,641 --> 00:52:06,891
♪She does not trust fate♪

956
00:52:06,891 --> 00:52:08,941
♪She does not pray to gods♪

957
00:52:08,941 --> 00:52:12,341
♪She grips the blade♪

958
00:52:12,341 --> 00:52:14,711
♪As geese fly south in winter♪

959
00:52:14,711 --> 00:52:16,811
♪She alone journeys north♪

960
00:52:16,811 --> 00:52:22,691
♪Seeking only a trace♪

961
00:52:23,771 --> 00:52:27,251
♪Of warmth♪

